{{Quote|Prince Aemon, the Dragonknight, may be the most famous Kingsguard who ever lived. How did he die? Defending Aegon the Unworthy from the brothers of a man who Aegon fed to his dogs. The man's crime? Sleeping with one of the many mistresses Aegon wasn't using. And the man was one of Aegon's own Kingsguard.|[[Bronn]]|The Kingsguard  (Histories &amp; Lore)}}
'''Bethany Bracken''' is an unseen character in ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]''. She is long dead before the start of the series, and thus is not expected to appear. Bethany Bracken was a member of [[House Bracken]] who lived during the reign of [[Aegon IV Targaryen]].
